\pard\plain \ltrch\loch {\f0\fs24\b0 The next few weeks were a chaotic mess of failed attempts and mounting frustration for Haruki. Determined to get Nagano and Honoka together before the end of summer, she threw herself into the role of matchmaker with all the subtlety of an elephant in an orchestra. Unfortunately, her efforts were met with one disaster after another.}
\par\pard\plain \sa180\sb180\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs24\b0 Haruki had thought her plan was foolproof. She convinced the PE teacher\hich\f0 \emdash \loch\f0 with a combination of flattery, persistence, and a well-timed offer to clean the equipment shed\hich\f0 \emdash \loch\f0 to schedule Class 1A and Class 2A for a joint volleyball session. Haruki\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s heart raced as she watched Nagano and his friends saunter onto the court, their laughter echoing across the gym. This was it. This was her chance.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 She quickly paired herself with Honoka, hoping to steer her toward Nagano\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s team. But Honoka, ever the shy and studious type, turned bright red at the mere suggestion of playing with the boys.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93I-I can\u8217\'92t!\u8221\'94 Honoka stammered, clutching her volleyball like a lifeline. \u8220\'93What if I mess up? What if they laugh at me?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93They won\u8217\'92t laugh at you!\u8221\'94 Haruki insisted, her voice a little too loud. \u8220\'93Nagano\u8217\'92s really nice, I promise!\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 But Honoka was already retreating to the safety of the girls\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92 team, leaving Haruki to face Nagano\u8217\'92s team alone. The match ended with Haruki getting hit in the face with the ball\hich\f0 \emdash \loch\f0 twice\hich\f0 \emdash \loch\f0 and Nagano teasing her mercilessly about her \u8220\'93unique\u8221\'94 playing style.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 Undeterred, Haruki hatched another plan. This time, she convinced Nagano to help her transport a stack of freshly printed papers from the Literature Club\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s print room to the editing department. She had heard Honoka mention something about editing, so surely this would work.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Why do I have to carry all these?\u8221\'94 Nagano grumbled, his arms laden with papers as they trudged down the hallway.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Because you\u8217\'92re strong and reliable,\u8221\'94 Haruki said, flashing him her most convincing smile. \u8220\'93And because I\u8217\'92ll buy you a soda later.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 Nagano rolled his eyes but didn\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92t complain further. Haruki\u8217\'92s heart raced as they approached the editing department. This was it. Honoka would be there, and they\u8217\'92d strike up a conversation, and everything would fall into place.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 But when they arrived, the room was empty except for a lone third-year student who looked up from their desk with a bored expression. \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Oh, the editing team\u8217\'92s in the other building today,\u8221\'94 they said. \u8220\'93You\u8217\'92re looking for the print department, right?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 Haruki\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s smile froze on her face. \u8220\'93Uh\u8230\'85 right. Thanks.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 Nagano shot her a suspicious look. \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Did you even know where we were going?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Of course I did!\u8221\'94 Haruki lied, her cheeks burning. \u8220\'93I just\u8230\'85 got the buildings mixed up. Let\u8217\'92s go!\u8221\'94}
\par\pard\plain \ltrch\loch {\f0\fs24\b0 By the time they found the correct department, Honoka was long gone, and Haruki was out two sodas.}
\par\pard\plain \sa180\sb180\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs24\b0 Haruki\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s third attempt was perhaps the most ambitious\hich\f0 \emdash \loch\f0 and the most disastrous. She convinced Honoka to join her after school, claiming they were going to \u8220\'93hang out\u8221\'94 with some of the boys from Class 2A. Honoka, though reluctant, agreed\hich\f0 \emdash \loch\f0 mostly because Haruki had promised to help her with a difficult math problem.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Are you sure this is a good idea?\u8221\'94 Honoka asked nervously as they waited outside the school gates. \u8220\'93I don\u8217\'92t really know these boys\u8230\'85\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93It\u8217\'92ll be fine!\u8221\'94 Haruki said, her voice a little too cheerful. \u8220\'93They\u8217\'92re really nice. And Nagano\u8217\'92s coming too!\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 Honoka\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s eyes widened. \u8220\'93Nagano?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Yeah!\u8221\'94 Haruki said, grinning. \u8220\'93He\u8217\'92s super cool. You\u8217\'92ll like him.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 But as the minutes ticked by, it became clear that something was wrong. The boys never showed up. After an hour of waiting, Honoka finally sighed and turned to Haruki. \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Maybe they\u8217\'92re not coming. Should we just go home?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 Haruki\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s heart sank. She had been so sure this would work. \u8220\'93Yeah\u8230\'85 I guess so.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 As they walked home, Haruki couldn\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92t help but feel a pang of guilt. Honoka had trusted her, and she had let her down. Again.}
